<L>__{interior bank. doors}
<A>__{ferris, cameron and sloane walk in. ferris is cocky and confident. sloane's still intoxicated with her freedom. cameron's having stomach trouble. ferris leads the way to an open teller window.}
<L>__{interior bank. teller}
<A>__{a woman about seventy with a silver blue beehive. it's about four inches higher the highest beehive you're ever seen. as she moves the beehive hits a small sign over her head. she's been at the bank since they opened. she smiles when she sees ferris.}
<C>__{teller}
<D>__{ferris bueller?}
<B>__{ferris}
<A>__{he's at the window. on either shoulder are cameron and sloane. ferris smiles. cameron blanches.}
